== 制作 ==
[[File:Jacqueline_Wilson.JPG|thumb]]
《垃圾箱里的婴儿》的剧本是根据杰奎琳·威尔逊2001年的同名[[小说|小说]]改编，海伦·布莱克曼编剧，她之前还曾为电视电影《乐土》（{{lang|en|''Pleasureland''}}）编剧。影片英国广播公司第一台和{{lang|en|[[CBBC|CBBC]]}}委托坎德尔娱乐公司制作，该公司专门制作面向[[儿童|儿童]]的[[电视节目|电视节目]]。根据《[[卫报|卫报]]》的报道，本片的定位是“英国广播公司第一台圣诞家庭（节目）阵容的重要组成部分”<ref>{{cite news | first = Leigh | last = Holmwood | title = Sneak preview of new BBC1 drama Dustbin Baby | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/organgrinder/2008/nov/26/dustbin-baby-bbc | publisher = ''The Guardian'' | date = 2008-11-26 | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | quote = a key part of BBC1's Christmas family line-up. | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140304144420/http://www.theguardian.com/media/organgrinder/2008/nov/26/dustbin-baby-bbc }}</ref>。布莱克莱表示在看完小说后就知道，这正是自己想要再创作的作品<ref name="Helen">{{cite news | first = Joe | last = Riley | title = Helen’s tale of woe | quote = knew it was something [she] had to write. | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120222001731/http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/views/liverpool-columnists/echo-columnists/2008/12/19/helen-s-tale-of-woe-100252-22509772/ | archivedate = 2012-02-22 | url = http://www.liverpoolecho.co.uk/views/liverpool-columnists/echo-columnists/2008/12/19/helen-s-tale-of-woe-100252-22509772/ | publisher = ''Liverpool Echo'' | date = 2008-12-19 | accessdate = 2008-12-21 }}</ref>。坎协尔公司的安妮·布罗根（{{lang|en|Anne Brogan}}）和梅拉妮·斯托克斯（{{lang|en|Melanie Stokes}}）以及{{lang|en|CBBC}}的苏·诺特（{{lang|en|Sue Nott}}）共同担任电影的[[执行制片人|执行制片人]]，朱莉娅·奥斯顿则是本片的[[制片人|制片人]]<ref name="adapts">{{cite news | first = Katherine | last = Rushton | title = BBC adapts Jacqueline Wilson for Christmas | archivedate = 2012-07-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120729061444/http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/multi-platform/news/bbc-adapts-jacqueline-wilson-for-christmas/1885025.article | url = http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/multi-platform/news/bbc-adapts-jacqueline-wilson-for-christmas/1885025.article | publisher = ''Broadcast'' | date = 2008-10-01 | accessdate = 2014-03-11 }}</ref>。导演朱丽叶·梅在电影拍摄期间有一对14岁大的双胞胎，觉得“对女主角艾普尔正好也是14岁这点……实在很感兴趣”，她相信自己“在某种程度上能够理解14岁大孩子的心思”<ref>May, Juliet (12 January 2009). ''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''. ''Dustbin Baby'' DVD. Kindle Entertainment/ITV DVD, event occurs at approximately 2:40.</ref>。

虽然威尔逊小说中“坚韧的现实主义”风格与[[达科塔·布鲁·理查兹|达科塔·布鲁·理查兹]]在《[[黄金罗盘|黄金罗盘]]》中扮演的[[莱拉贝诺夸|莱拉贝诺夸]]有很大不同，但她还是很乐意出演艾普尔一角<ref name="interview" />。她表示自己能够真正将威尔逊小说中的人物联系起来，但又发现艾普尔是个和自己很不一样的人<ref name="interview" />。威尔逊之前曾看过理查兹在《黄金罗盘》中的表演，觉得她会很适合出演《垃圾箱里的婴儿》<ref>Wilson, Jacqueline (12 January 2009). ''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''. ''Dustbin Baby'' DVD. Kindle Entertainment/ITV DVD, event occurs at approximately 7:37.</ref>。理查兹扮演的是14岁时的艾普尔，片中由其他演员出演了该角色年纪更小时的镜头。如电影拍摄期间年仅5岁的露西·哈钦森诠释的就是除婴儿时期外最年幼版本的艾普尔。导演朱丽叶·梅称赞她是自己所遇到过最了不起的五岁演员之一，表示其表演浑然天成，非常自然<ref>May, Juliet (12 January 2009). ''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''. ''Dustbin Baby'' DVD. Kindle Entertainment/ITV DVD, event occurs at approximately 5:00.</ref>。亚历山德拉·休伊特饰演童年时期的艾普尔，梅也称赞她的表演令人信服<ref>May, Juliet (12 January 2009). ''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''. ''Dustbin Baby'' DVD. Kindle Entertainment/ITV DVD, event occurs at approximately 5:57.</ref>。休伊特扮演的是八岁大的艾普尔，不过电影拍摄期间她已经十岁<ref>Hewitt, Alexandra. (12 January 2009). ''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''. ''Dustbin Baby'' DVD. Kindle Entertainment/ITV DVD, event occurs at approximately 6:45.</ref>。

茱丽叶特·斯蒂文森表示，自己出演马里昂一角一方面是因为她当时也有个14岁的女儿，另一方面她还觉得自己和这个角色在一定程度上心有灵犀<ref name="interview">{{cite news | first = Bernadette | last = McNulty | title = Dustbin Baby | url = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/3851819/Dustbin-Baby.html | publisher = ''The Telegraph'' | date = 2008-12-19 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-11-10 | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121110232032/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/tvandradio/3851819/Dustbin-Baby.html }}</ref>。大卫·海格参加《垃圾箱里的婴儿》演出期间还出演了另外三部电视节目挣钱养家。他觉得自己很适合出演这个有些[[友情客串|客串]]性质的角色<ref name="Loot">{{cite news | first = Viv | last = Hardwick | title = Loot of laughs | url = http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/leisure/entertainment/theatre/features/4049301.Loot_of_laughs/ | publisher = ''The Northern Echo'' | date = 2009-01-15 | accessdate = 2012-10-05 | archivedate = 2012-10-05 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121005033525/http://www.thenorthernecho.co.uk/leisure/entertainment/theatre/features/4049301.Loot_of_laughs/ }}</ref>。影片的拍摄工作于2008年夏<ref name="Loot" />在[[伦敦|伦敦]]及周边地区进行，还有些外景在[[赫特福德郡|赫特福德郡]][[哈特菲尔德|哈特菲尔德]]的[[哈特菲尔德庄园|哈特菲尔德庄园]]（{{lang|en|Hatfield House}}）以及[[巴尼特区|巴尼特区]]的[[巴尼特|巴尼特]]（{{lang|en|Barnet}}）拍摄<ref name="Kindle">{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-03-12 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120312051932/http://www.kindleentertainment.com/completedproductions.html | url = http://www.kindleentertainment.com/completedproductions.html | title = Dustbin Baby | publisher = Kindle Entertainment | accessdate = 2014-03-11 }}</ref>。威尔逊曾在电影拍摄完成前接受[[圖書館採訪|采访]]时表示自己对小说能够由如此出众的演员和制作团队搬上银幕深感荣幸，并对影片充满期待<ref name="Kindle" />。

[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]有意寻找一位患有亚斯伯格症候群的女演员来出演波比一角。丽兹·克拉克的母亲在一个自闭症网站上看到了广告，于是让自己的女儿参加了试镜，后者成功获得了这个角色，这也是她的银幕处女作<ref name="asperger">{{cite news | title = Fame for actress with Asperger syndrome | archivedate = 2013-01-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130130055612/http://www.bbc.co.uk/shropshire/content/articles/2008/09/16/aspergers_actress_feature.shtml | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/shropshire/content/articles/2008/09/16/aspergers_actress_feature.shtml | publisher = BBC | date = 2008-08-16 | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。克拉克是第一位真的患有亚斯伯格症候群，同时又扮演一位患有该疾病角色的女演员，她从此后开始与自己的母亲一起奔走呼号，反对由没有患有这一病症的演员来饰演这样的角色。她表示：“我的亚斯伯格症起初给电影的拍摄带来了困难，例如面对故事板突然发出的噪音等，但我很快就会集中精神开始表演，并且全神贯注，不会受到任何干扰。”<ref>{{cite news | title = Mentally disabled actors are victims of modern 'blacking-up', says campaigner | author = Hill, Amelia | newspaper = The Observer | date = 2009-11-15 | archivedate = 2014-03-11 | deadurl = no | quote = My Asperger's made some things on the film set difficult at first, like dealing with the sudden noise of the storyboard, but I was soon so focused on acting that I didn't notice anything else. | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140311080802/http://www.theguardian.com/society/2009/nov/15/disabled-actors-television-campaign | url = http://www.theguardian.com/society/2009/nov/15/disabled-actors-television-campaign | accessdate = 2014-03-11 }}</ref>。

== 主题 ==
[[File:Dustbin_Baby-_April.jpg|thumb]]
布莱克曼表示自己是一次看完了原著小说并感动得流下了眼泪<ref name="Helen" />。电影的主题包括霸凌、青少年犯罪、[[家庭暴力|家庭暴力]]、意外[[怀孕|怀孕]]和[[青少年|青少年焦虑]]<ref name="Helen" />。在布莱克莱看来，艾普尔“寻找生母那令人心碎的旅程讲述的也是她勇敢接受他人爱的过程”<ref name="Helen" />。《[[独立报|独立报]]》的汤姆·萨特克利夫（{{lang|en|Tom Sutcliffe}}）在谈及家庭剧的忌讳主题限制时表示，本片中诉说的生活没有那么多脏话，也没有对药品的滥用，当孩子们的床前夜间出现一道黑影时，也不是哪个家中的主宰要来行使什么可怕的[[初夜权|初夜权]]，因为如果有这些内容的话，这就变成了一部成人剧情片<ref name="independent">{{cite news | first = Tom | last = Sutcliffe | title = The Weekend's Television | archivedate = 2012-10-25 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121025033805/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/the-weekends-television-lark-rise-to-candleford-sun-bbc1brdustbin-baby-sun-bbc1brbrrussell-brands-christmas-ponderland-sun-channel-4br-1207076.html | url = http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/tv/reviews/the-weekends-television-lark-rise-to-candleford-sun-bbc1brdustbin-baby-sun-bbc1brbrrussell-brands-christmas-ponderland-sun-channel-4br-1207076.html | publisher = ''The Independent'' | date = 2008-12-22 | accessdate = 2014-03-11 }}</ref>。影片还通过波比一角涉及了亚斯伯格症候群的主题。英国广播公司声称，该角色的扮演者克拉克由于自己就患有这一疾病，因此可以给予角色“一个独特的视角”<ref name="asperger" />。斯蒂文森对电影的主题加以总结，称这个故事的核心就是马里昂发现自己爱这个女孩。对于一个人来说，发现自己觉得另一个人比自己还要重要，这是一件很了不起的事。这也是为人父母了不起的地方，你会比起关心自己来更关心你的孩子<ref name="interview" />。

威尔逊在以《垃圾箱里的婴儿》幕后故事为主要内容的纪录片《垃圾箱的背后：〈垃圾箱的婴儿〉制作》（{{lang|en|''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''}}）中表示，许多人，许多许多人都会发现片中有关收养的核心主题，那些14岁的孩子们会开始看着自己的父母，心里琢磨着他们和自己一点都不像，大家都会幻想一把自己是不是从哪儿收养的之类，所以在威尔逊看来，对于一位青少年来说，质问、怀疑自己的来历实在是一件很常见的事情<ref>Wilson, Jacqueline.  (12 January 2009). ''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''. ''Dustbin Baby'' DVD. Kindle Entertainment/ITV DVD, event occurs at approximately 3:33.</ref>。理查兹表示，她喜欢片中艾普尔“踏上旅程寻找自我”的理念，因为有许多在她这个年纪的人“都会试图这么做，因为这个时候，他们都开始对自我产生怀疑，心中有了疑问”<ref>[[达科塔·布鲁·理查兹|Richards, Dakota Blue]]. (12 January 2009). ''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''. ''Dustbin Baby'' DVD. Kindle Entertainment/ITV DVD, event occurs at approximately 4:40.</ref>。理查兹还认为，艾普尔的纸娃娃相当于一个符号，这个符号可以用不同的东西代替，她还是同样一个人，只不过她的生命由于遇到了不同的人和事而有了不同的色彩<ref>Richards, Dakota Blue. (12 January 2009). ''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''. ''Dustbin Baby'' DVD. Kindle Entertainment/ITV DVD, event occurs at approximately 4:00.</ref>。在片中诠释童年时期艾普尔的亚历山德拉·休伊特则表示，那些纸娃娃才是艾普尔“真正的[[朋友|朋友]]”<ref name="Hewitt">Hewitt, Alexandra. (12 January 2009). ''Behind the Bin: The Making of Dustbin Baby''. ''Dustbin Baby'' DVD. Kindle Entertainment/ITV DVD, event occurs at approximately 4:48.</ref>。

斯蒂文森形容马里昂这个角色“倔强、孤独而且会胡思乱想”，认为她因长期独自一人而“变得很愚蠢和古怪”。艾普尔一角的出现让马里昂需要一下子学会为人父母，这很不容易，很容易出错，所以当艾普尔离家出走时，马里昂的心里充满了自责和焦虑<ref name="interview" />。她还把自己现实生活中养育孩子所遇到的困难与马里昂相比，称她已经有了14年的经验，所以在这方面可以比自己饰演的角色更得心应手<ref name="interview" />。理查兹则表示，自己完全没有体会过寄宿学校和儿童福利院的生活，艾普尔觉得自己在这个世界上无依无靠，所以急切地想要知道自己到底是谁<ref name="interview" />。

== 反响 ==
威尔逊在看过《垃圾箱里的婴儿》的前期试映后称，这是根据自己作品改编的电影中最出色的一部<ref name="Helen" />。海格表示本片是他暑期出演的多部作品中自己最喜欢的一部，称赞“这是个非常出众的故事，拍得很感人。我觉得茱丽叶特·斯蒂文森在片中非常风趣，也非常让人感动”<ref name="Loot" />。影评人也作出了正面回应。《[[泰晤士报|泰晤士报]]》在大卫·查特（{{lang|en|David Chater}}）认为这是影片播出当天最值得一看的电视节目，这部优秀的电影是[[圣诞节|圣诞节]]的美妙惊喜<ref>{{cite news | first = David | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2011-06-16 | last = Chater | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110616142603/http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/tv_and_radio/article5358447.ece | url = http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/tv_and_radio/article5358447.ece | title = TV Choice | publisher = ''The Times'' | date = 2008-12-20 | accessdate = 2011-06-16 | location = London }}</ref>。《[[每日电讯报|每日电讯报]]》也形容欣赏本片是一次“难得的享受”，是一部青少年可以与父母一起观看的好节目<ref name="interview" />。电影的制片人朱莉娅·奥斯顿也有同样看法，称这部电影适合父母与孩子们一起观看，并将因此产生许多的共同话题<ref name="adapts" />。《[[独立报|独立报]]》的汤姆·萨特克利夫认为，斯蒂文森成功地扮演了这样一个对过去远比对现在要感到如意自在的女性，并且她的表演比达科塔·布鲁·理查兹出演的艾普尔更加到位。不过他也批评影片的情况不够可信，认为剧情可能远不及现实生活中那样残酷，但面对片尾的和解，观众还是会产生真切的情感<ref name="independent" />。《卫报》的尤安·弗格森（{{lang|en|Euan Ferguson}}）在文章中认为，影片有些高度理想化，斯蒂文森扮演的角色更是如此，一定程度上就像是《[[春风不化雨|春风不化雨]]》（{{lang|en|''The Prime of Miss Jean Brodie''}}）中女主角简·布罗迪（{{lang|en|Jean Brodie}}）的升级版<ref>{{cite news | first = Euan | last = Ferguson | title = Hail these Plasticine scene stealers | url = http://www.theguardian.com/culture/2008/dec/28/wallace-and-gromit-blackadder | publisher = ''The Guardian'' | date = 2008-12-28 | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | archivedate = 2014-03-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140311144158/http://www.theguardian.com/culture/2008/dec/28/wallace-and-gromit-blackadder }}</ref>。《垃圾箱里的婴儿》在英国广播公司第一台首播时一共吸引了230万观众收看，收获了15.4%的收视率<ref>{{cite news | first = Chris | last = Curtis | title = BBC1/ITV1 boosted by Xmas dramas | url = http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/multi-platform/news/bbc1/itv1-boosted-by-xmas-dramas/1955939.article | publisher = ''Broadcast'' | date = 2008-12-22 | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | archive-date = 2014-03-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140311180515/http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/multi-platform/news/bbc1/itv1-boosted-by-xmas-dramas/1955939.article | dead-url = no |subscription=yes}}</ref>。

== 荣誉 ==
在2009年的第37届国际艾美奖儿童和青年类电视节目评选中，《垃圾箱的婴儿》是最终入围的四部儿童电视节目之一。这年英国获得的提名数量达到九项，超过其他任何国家和地区<ref>{{cite news | title = Kissinger Lined Up for International Emmys, Nominees Announced | author = Daswani, Mansha | publisher = WorldScreen.com |subscription=yes | date = 2009-10-05 | url = http://www.worldscreen.com/articles/display/22771 | accessdate = 2009-10-05 | archive-date = 2009-10-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091006131756/http://www.worldscreen.com/articles/display/22771 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。最终本片成功拿下了该奖，是英国在2009年获得的六项国际艾美奖之一，也是英国广播公司获得的三项国际艾美奖之一<ref>{{cite news | title = Sir David Frost wins International Emmy in ceremony dominated by Brits | author = Robinson, James | newspaper = The Guardian | date = 2009-11-24 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-03-11 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140311150335/http://www.theguardian.com/media/2009/nov/24/sir-david-frost-emmy | url = http://www.theguardian.com/media/2009/nov/24/sir-david-frost-emmy | accessdate = 2014-03-11 }}</ref>。《垃圾箱里的婴儿》还与同样由英国广播公司制作的《[[珍姐科幻大冒险|珍姐科幻大冒险]]》、[[威尔斯第四台|威尔斯第四台]]的另一个节目以及有关男孩乐队{{lang|en|[[US5|US5]]}}的[[网络电视|网上]]节目一起获得了[[英国电影和电视艺术学院|英国儿童电影和电视艺术学院]]的剧情的电视节目提名<ref>{{cite news | title = Hammond up for children's Bafta | publisher = BBC | date = 2009-10-27 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8327527.stm | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | archivedate = 2014-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140303001143/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8327527.stm | deadurl = no }}</ref>。不过最终在11月29日举行的颁奖典礼上胜出的是威尔斯第四台的节目<ref name="Hammond wins">{{cite news | title = Richard Hammond wins Bafta for best presenter | publisher = BBC | date = 2009-11-30 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8385684.stm | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | archivedate = 2009-12-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091203120231/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8385684.stm | deadurl = no }}</ref>。布莱克莱因本片的编剧工作获英国儿童电影和电视艺术学院的最佳编剧提名<ref>{{cite news | title = The Sarah Jane Adventures nominated for Bafta | author = Hemley, Matthew | newspaper = The Stage | date = 2009-10-27 | url = http://www.thestage.co.uk/news/2009/10/the-sarah-jane-adventures-nominated-for-bafta/ | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | archive-date = 2014-03-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140311184632/http://www.thestage.co.uk/news/2009/10/the-sarah-jane-adventures-nominated-for-bafta/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>，并且最终也成功胜出<ref name="Hammond wins" />。影片还进入了英国儿童电影和电视艺术学院的电视节目类儿童投票角逐，由七到十四岁儿童投票选择自己最喜欢的电视节目，入围作品包括《[[蓝色彼得|蓝色彼得]]》、《[[孟汉娜|孟汉娜]]》、《[[飞哥与小佛|飞哥与小佛]]》、《[[爱卡莉|爱卡莉]]》和《[[海绵宝宝|海绵宝宝]]》等<ref>{{cite news | title = BAFTA Kids' Nominations Announced | author = Daswani, Mansha | publisher = WorldScreen.com |subscription=yes | date = 2009-10-27 | url = http://www.worldscreen.com/articles/display/23073 | accessdate = 2010-02-16 | archive-date = 2009-11-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091103164904/http://www.worldscreen.com/articles/display/23073 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，不过最终未能胜出<ref name="Hammond wins" />。

2010年2月，《垃圾箱里的婴儿》获得了2010年儿童银幕奖面向家庭观众类最佳单集、特别节目或电视电影奖<ref>{{cite news | title = KidScreen Awards Winners Announced | author = Brzoznowski, Kristin | publisher = WorldScreen.com |subscription=yes | date = 2010-02-12 | url = http://www.worldscreen.com/articles/display/24349 | accessdate = 2010-02-16 | archive-date = 2010-02-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100215204622/http://www.worldscreen.com/articles/display/24349 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，还赢得了创新人才奖最佳演技奖。英国广播公司儿童台总裁乔·古德温表示，他非常高興电视台节目的原创性和对全世界儿童的启发可以获得国际性的认可，并特别为电视台能够赢得剧情类和写实类节目奖项感到满意，因为这一直是，也永远都将是英国广播公司儿童台独特的核心组成部分<ref>{{cite news | title = CBBC enjoys success at KidScreen Awards | author = Laughlin, Andrew | publisher = Digital Spy | date = 2010-02-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121018015253/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/media/news/a203249/cbbc-enjoys-success-at-kidscreen-awards.html | url = http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/media/news/a203249/cbbc-enjoys-success-at-kidscreen-awards.html | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | archivedate = 2012-10-18 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2012-08-13 | url = http://kidscreen.com/2010/02/11/kidscreenawardswinners-20100211/ | title = And the inaugural KidScreen Awards winners are... | author = Castleman, Lana | date = 2010-02-11 | publisher = KidScreen | accessdate = 2014-03-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120813204649/http://kidscreen.com/2010/02/11/kidscreenawardswinners-20100211/ }}</ref>。

